column5: Just got back from Pine falls. Fished two days, and all three of us are coming back with Master anglers. Caught prolly 150 fish in 2 days. Caught a 11.6, 10.6, and a 10.5. All were 30 inches. So it was a great trip. Just wanted to know if the weight caculator is accurate on this site. That is how I figured the weight of our fish.
